feedback.question: Can you describe a situation where you used conditional formatting effectively?
feedback.user_answer: I used conditional formatting in Excel to highlight employee attendance below 80% in red and performance scores above 90% in green. This made it easy for management to quickly identify areas needing attention and recognize high performers, saving review time and improving decision-making.
